OL,3,CReeves faces Budget 'groundhog day'
OL,4,Cwithout bold action, says IFS
OL,6,FRachel Reeves needs to be "bold" when
OL,7,Fshe delivers her Budget or face
OL,8,F"groundhog day" with more cuts or tax
OL,9,Frises next year, a think tank has
OL,10,Fwarned.
OL,12,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS)
OL,13,Fsaid it expected the Chancellor would
OL,14,Fneed to find at least #22 billion next
OL,15,Fmonth, thanks to rising borrowing
OL,16,Fcosts, weaker growth forecasts and
OL,17,Fspending commitments made since the
OL,18,Fspring.
