OL,3,CReeves faces Budget 'groundhog day'
OL,4,Cwithout bold action, says IFS
OL,6,FIFS director Helen Miller said: "For
OL,7,FRachel Reeves, the Budget will feel
OL,8,Flike groundhog day."
OL,10,FShe added that the situation was "to a
OL,11,Flarge extent" of the Chancellor's own
OL,12,Fmaking, after choosing to "operate her
OL,13,Ffiscal rules with such teeny tiny
OL,14,Fheadroom" that left her exposed to
OL,15,F"run-of-the-mill forecast changes".
OL,17,FThe IFS said implementing a larger
OL,18,Ffiscal consolidation in November would
OL,19,Fbe "the most straightforward route" to
OL,20,Favoiding similar challenges in future
OL,21,Fyears.
